    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Agency PAYGO Act of 2013 - Requires the Administrator of the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) to include in a proposed rule that limits greenhouse gas emissions and imposes increased costs on other agencies an offset from funds available to the Administrator for all projected increased costs that the proposed rule would impose on other agencies. </p> <p> Prohibits the Administrator from finalizing such a proposed rule unless such an offset is provided.<BR> <BR> </p>]]></text>
